# 9. Non Goals

Agents must not attempt to build:

a full LMS  
automatic scanning of all Drive documents  
complex recommendation engines  
background crawling of user data

Focus only on the core assignment-to-portal workflow.

---

# 10. Documentation Requirements

README must always include:

project description  
setup instructions  
environment variables  
API configuration steps  
development commands

Agents must update documentation when setup changes.

---

# 11. Testing Guidelines

When possible:

add small functional tests  
test API routes independently  
verify API error handling

Agents must avoid introducing breaking changes.

---

# 12. Design Principles

The application should follow these principles:

Clarity over complexity  
Minimal access to user data  
Small composable modules  
Predictable structured AI outputs

The final system should feel like a focused academic tool rather than a generic productivity app.

